You need to convert the models with the quantization flags for toco (https://www.tensorflow.org/performance/quantization)

--input_format=TENSORFLOW_GRAPHDEF 
--inference_type=QUANTIZED_UINT8
--output_format=TFLITE  
--input_shapes=1,224,224,3 
--input_arrays=input 
--output_arrays=MobilenetV1/Predictions/Reshape_1
--std_values=128
--mean_values=128

Also looking at the end of your output that you have pasted it looks like you have some formatting errors in you bash command line.

body:
You need to convert the models with the quantization flags for toco (https://www.tensorflow.org/performance/quantization)

```
--input_format=TENSORFLOW_GRAPHDEF 
--inference_type=QUANTIZED_UINT8
--output_format=TFLITE  
--input_shapes=1,224,224,3 
--input_arrays=input 
--output_arrays=MobilenetV1/Predictions/Reshape_1
--std_values=128
--mean_values=128
```

Also looking at the end of your output that you have pasted it looks like you have some formatting errors in you bash command line.
